The paper discusses the development of a data visualization recommender system, which involves aspects of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), information retrieval (cs.IR), and database systems (cs.DB). The system also incorporates decision-making algorithms and classification hierarchies, which are common in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
